It is highly recommended to use a remote client of Forge on your local machine
You can download our free remote clients from

https://developer.arm.com/tools-and-software/server-and-hpc/arm-architecture-tools/downloads/download-arm-forge

Please view the slides for instructions on how to run these examples

If you wish to preview features of the upcoming release, find the appropriate file for your operating system from
/opt/arm/forge/20.0-rc4/installers
located on this machine and scp it back to your local machine

